    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "But Paderewski's success has been greater than any of these.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Americans are said to be fickle; but although Paderewski no longer is a novelty, his name still is the one with which to fill a concert hall from floor to roof.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Why this is so is no secret.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Hear him and you will understand the reason.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "To a technique which does not hesitate at anything and an industry that flinches at nothing-no one practices more assiduously than he-he adds the soul of a poet and the strength of an athlete.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000004_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000004_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Therefore he combines poetry with force; and back of both is thought-intellectual capacity.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "It represents the net receipts of one virtuoso for one concert tour, and is believed to be the largest actual amount ever earned in this country by an artist, whether singer or player, in a single season.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "This check is drawn to the order of Ignace j Paderewski.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "An opinion regarding the piano by a man who by playing it can earn so large a sum, and earn it because he is the greatest living exponent of pianoforte playing, would seem worth having.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Paderewski believes that, save in one respect, the pianoforte has reached perfection and is incapable of further improvement.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "He does not think that anything more should be done to add to its volume of tone.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000006_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000006_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "If anything, he considers this too great and the instrument too loud already.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000006_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000006_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Instead of more power, rather less would be satisfactory.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000006_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000006_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Wherein, however, he considers the instrument still lacking, notwithstanding its wonderful development during the last century, is in its capacity for sustained tone-for holding a long drawn out tone with the facility of the violin, for example.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000006_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000006_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "He is convinced, however, that the means of imparting this capacity for sustaining tone to the pianoforte will be discovered in due time and that the invention probably will be made in this country.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000006_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000006_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "After all, it remains the greatest of all solo instruments, because, within the smallest compass and with the simplest means of control, it has the range of an orchestra.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000006_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000006_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "For this reason it is the most popular of instruments and, in its manufacture, extends from the polished dry goods box with internal organs of iron, wire and felt and with a glistening row of celluloid teeth ready to bite as soon as ever the lid is raised, to the highest class concert grand.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "The \"Piano Doctor.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "We who have our pianofortes in our own homes and are content with an occasional visit from the tuner, little dream of the care bestowed upon the instrument on which an artist like Paderewski plays. Instrument?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "True, these pianos do not have their throats sprayed on the slightest possible occasion, but they are carefully protected against extremes of heat and cold, and, while the prima donna consults her physician only at intervals, a \"piano doctor\" is in constant attendance on these instruments.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Paderewski's \"piano doctor\" has traveled with him for several seasons, occupying the same private car and practically living with him during the entire tour.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "He was with him on the tour, in fact at his table at breakfast with him, when his special train was run on to an open siding near East Syracuse and left the track, Paderewski being thrown forward on his hands against the table and straining the muscles of one arm so severely that he was obliged to cancel his remaining engagements.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "His record concert was at dallas texas, some years ago, when the receipts were nine thousand dollars.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000009_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000009_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Then he realized what had happened, smiled and continued amid laughter and applause.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Pianofortes on Their Travels.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "But to return to the pianofortes on tour.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "He rarely plays when the car is in motion.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000011_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000011_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Of the other three instruments, the two he liked best were sent to his hotel, where during four days preceding his first concert, he practiced from seven to eight hours a day, notifying the \"doctor\" twenty four hours in advance which pianoforte he would use.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "The pianist's route took him from San Francisco to Oakland, San Jose, and portland oregon.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Paderewski: \"Well, 'Doctor,' it sounded all right to night, didn't it?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Paderewski: \"Well, then, please pass me the bread.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "There never has been occasion to record what would happen if the \"doctor\" were to say, \"No, sir.\" For he always has been able to answer in the affirmative, with the most scrupulous regard for veracity.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Paderewski is as careful to play his best in the least important place in which he gives a concert as he is in New York.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "This high sense of duty toward his public accounts in part for his supremacy among pianists Paderewski is not a mere virtuoso.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "He is a man of fine intellectual gifts who plays the piano like a poet.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000017_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000017_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "His knowledge of the history of his native land, Poland, and of its literature is said to be quite wonderful.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000017_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000017_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Chopin, also a Pole, he idolizes and regards as far and away the greatest composer for the piano.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "When the amusing little dialogue at the supper table, which I have recorded, takes place, the pianoforte which the virtuoso has used at his concert already will be on the way to its next destination.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000018_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000018_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "For it is part of the \"doctor's\" duty to see it safely out of the hall and onto the train before rejoining the party on the private car.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "The instrument is not boxed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000018_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000018_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "The legs are removed and then a carefully fitted canvas is drawn over the body and held in place by straps.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000018_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000018_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "The body is slid out of the hall and slowly let down onto a specially constructed eight wheel skid, swung low, so as to be as nearly as possible on a level with the platform.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000018_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000018_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "This skid is part of the outfit of the tour.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000018_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000018_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "The record time for detaching the legs of the pianoforte, covering the body, removing the instrument from the stage and having it on the skid ready to start for the station, is seven minutes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "The instruments never are set up except under the \"doctor's\" personal supervision.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Before each concert the pianoforte on which Paderewski is to play is carefully gone over and put in perfect condition-tuned and, if necessary, regulated, and this no matter how recently he may have used it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Defects so trifling that neither an ordinary player nor the public would notice them, would jar on the sensitive ear and nerves of the virtuoso.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000020_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000020_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Sometimes the instrument has been exposed to such a low temperature that frost is found to have formed not only on the lid, but even on the iron plate inside.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000020_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000020_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "In such cases the pianoforte is set up and, after the film of frost has been scraped off, is allowed to thaw out slowly and naturally before it is touched for tuning or regulating.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "The \"doctor\" relies on local help for getting the pianoforte from the skid to the stage and back again.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000021_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000021_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "The \"doctor\" went among them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "\"What are you doing?\" he asked.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "\"Want a job?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "At last, however, a band of twenty \"colored gentlemen\" was secured in the hope that muscle and quantity would make up for lack of quality. But never before has a high grade pianoforte been in such imminent peril.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "But the descent!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000026_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000026_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "The \"doctor,\" Emil c Fischer, stood at the top of the stairs directing; j e Francke, the treasurer of the tour, below.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000026_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000026_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Around the latter fell a shower of fragments from the wall, the rail, the posts; and at one time it seemed as if the whole banister would give way and the pianoforte crash in splinters on the floor.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000026_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000026_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "There were other moments of suspense, for the pianoforte as well as for the two watchers, who drew a long breath when the instrument safely was on the skid.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Fortunately such untoward incidents are forgotten in the general atmosphere of good humor which the pianist diffuses about him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000027_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000027_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "He enjoys his little joke.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000027_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000027_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "During the last tour he handed a photograph of himself to mr Francke inscribed: \"To the future Governor of Hoboken.\" At the Auditorium hotel, Chicago, Millward Adams' brother, about leaving on a trip, asked for an autograph.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000027_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000027_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Paderewski, quick as a flash, wrote:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54188_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54188/5840_54188_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Paderewski travels on a special train.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54193_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54193/5840_54193_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "thirteen",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54193_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54193/5840_54193_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "A NOTE ON CHAMBER MUSIC",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54193_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54193/5840_54193_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Lovers of chamber music form an extremely refined and cultured class, and, like all highly refined and cultured people, are very conservative.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54193_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54193/5840_54193_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "They are the purists among music lovers, the last people who would care to see the classical forms abandoned, and who would be disturbed, not to say shocked, by any great departure from the sonata form.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54193_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54193/5840_54193_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "For the string quartet is to chamber music what the symphony is to orchestra and the sonata to the pianoforte-is, in fact, a sonata for two violins, viola and violoncello, just as the symphony is a sonata for orchestra.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54193_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54193/5840_54193_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Oddly enough, a pianoforte solo is more effective in a large hall than a string quartet, although the latter employs four times as many instruments; and the same is true of those pieces of chamber music in which the pianoforte is used, such as sonatas for pianoforte and violin or violoncello, pianoforte trios, quartets, quintets, and so on.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54193_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54193/5840_54193_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Paderewski plays in Carnegie Hall, and, I am sure, would be equally effective in the Opera House.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54193_000004_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54193/5840_54193_000004_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "But an organization of chamber music players would be lost in either place.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5840_54193_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5840/54193/5840_54193_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5840",
        "content": "Indeed, compared with the opera, the orchestra and even with the pianoforte, chamber music requires a setting like a jewel.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
